eating mac and cheese?

18:04.333 --> 18:06.000
-What?
-[imitates Malcolm] "What?"

18:06.833 --> 18:08.416
-I'm not.
-Don't fucking lie!

18:08.500 --> 18:10.666
-You literally just got seconds.
-No, I didn't.

18:10.750 --> 18:12.125
