while eating mac and cheese?

18:16.583 --> 18:18.625
-Abuse you?
-Mac and cheese I fucking made you.

18:18.708 --> 18:20.375
-Abuse you?
-Verbally abuse me.

18:20.458 --> 18:22.875
Thanks for the clarification.
