19:00.041 --> 19:01.791
-Not at my expense.
-Actually, it is.

19:01.875 --> 19:03.916
Despite how you fucking
feel about it, it is my job.

19:04.000 --> 19:06.000
-You'd never forget to thank her.
-Jesus Christ!

19:06.083 --> 19:08.041
-You wouldn't.
-'Cause she's psychotic.

19:08.125 --> 19:09.750
No, because she would flip the fuck out

19:09.833 --> 19:13.875
