22:11.791 --> 22:12.791
Can I kiss you?

22:13.583 --> 22:14.583
No.

22:17.250 --> 22:20.125
-Are you sure?
-Mm-hmm.

22:22.125 --> 22:23.166
[Malcolm sighs]

22:23.250 --> 22:26.125
